# Django API origin (no trailing slash). Default in code: http://127.0.0.1:8000
#
# This repo ships `.env.development` → hosted API for `npm run dev`, and `.env.production` for `vite build`.
# To use a local Django server during dev instead, create `.env.development.local` (gitignored) with:
# VITE_API_BASE=http://127.0.0.1:8000
VITE_API_BASE=http://127.0.0.1:8000

# Optional: Google Maps JavaScript API key (Maps JavaScript API + Places API for address suggestions on checkout/profile maps).
# If unset, the app uses OpenStreetMap (Leaflet) for tracking maps and Nominatim for address search.
# VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
